        <section class="exam-programs-section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Exam Preparation Programs</h2>
            
            <div class="exam-grid">
                <div class="exam-card border-blue">
                    <h3>🗓️ Flexible Formats</h3>
                    <p>
                        Offering both <strong>1-on-1 individual</strong> and <strong>group sessions</strong>. Choose between an <strong>8-week accelerated</strong> crash course or a comprehensive <strong>16-week standard</strong> program tailored to your exam timeline.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="exam-card border-green">
                    <h3>📊 Mock Exams & Analysis</h3>
                    <p>
                        Every student receives <strong>5 free mock exams</strong> simulating real test conditions, followed by comprehensive <strong>result evaluation reports</strong> to pinpoint areas for improvement.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="exam-card border-orange">
                    <h3>🎯 Strategic Problem Solving</h3>
                    <p>
                        Includes <strong>personalized homework</strong> and guided solving sessions. Students master the effective use of <strong>TI and Desmos calculators</strong>, saving crucial time during exams.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="exam-card border-purple">
                    <h3>⭐ The Guarantee</h3>
                    <p>
                        Start with a completely <strong>Free Trial Lesson</strong> to experience the methodology firsthand. I stand by a strict <strong>Success Guarantee</strong> for students who complete the required program milestones.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="stem-intro">
            <h1>STEM Tutoring & Lecturing</h1>
            <p>
                I specialize in providing high-quality, structured tutoring for high school and university students across international curricula. My approach focuses on deep conceptual understanding and rigorous problem-solving.
            </p>
            
            <div class="highlight-badges">
                <div class="feature-badge" style="background: #eff6ff; color: #1d4ed8; border-color: #bfdbfe;">
                    🌍 English & Turkish
                </div>
                <div class="feature-badge" style="background: #f0fdf4; color: #15803d; border-color: #bbf7d0;">
                    💻 100% Online
                </div>
                <div class="feature-badge" style="background: #fef2f2; color: #b91c1c; border-color: #fecaca;">
                    ⏱️ 90-Minute Blocks
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="content">
            <div class="curriculum-grid">
                
                <div class="curriculum-box border-left-blue">
                    <h3>AP (Advanced Placement)</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Mathematics:</strong> Calculus AB & BC, Statistics</li>
                        <li><strong>Physics:</strong> Physics 1, 2, and Physics C (Mechanics & E&M)</li>
                        <li><strong>Computer Science:</strong> Computer Science A, Computer Science Principles</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="curriculum-box border-left-red">
                    <h3>IB (International Baccalaureate)</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Mathematics:</strong> Analysis and Approaches (AA), Applications and Interpretation (AI) - HL & SL</li>
                        <li><strong>Physics:</strong> Higher Level (HL) & Standard Level (SL)</li>
                        <li><strong>Computer Science:</strong> Higher Level (HL) & Standard Level (SL)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="curriculum-box border-left-orange">
                    <h3>SAT Preparation</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Mathematics:</strong> Comprehensive SAT Math preparation, advanced problem-solving, and timing strategies.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="curriculum-box border-left-green">
                    <h3>University Math & Physics</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Core Calculus & Analysis:</strong> Calculus I-II-III (Multivariable), Advanced Calculus, Real Analysis, Complex Analysis</li>
                        <li><strong>Algebra & Geometry:</strong> Linear Algebra, Abstract Algebra, Differential Geometry</li>
                        <li><strong>Applied & Engineering Math:</strong> Ordinary & Partial Differential Equations (ODE & PDE), Numerical Analysis, Engineering Mathematics, Probability & Statistics</li>
                        <li><strong>Physics:</strong> University General Physics (Mechanics & Electromagnetism)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="curriculum-box border-left-purple">
                    <h3>University Computer Science</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Programming Languages:</strong> Python, C, C++, Java</li>
                        <li><strong>Core CS & Theory:</strong> Data Structures, Algorithm Design, Automata Theory, Discrete Mathematics</li>
                        <li><strong>Systems & Hardware:</strong> Database Systems, Computer Architecture, Circuit Design</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>
